OL,3,CGuernsey FC miss out on promotion
OL,4,Cafter play-off final defeat
OL,6,FGuernsey FC have missed the chance for
OL,7,Fan immediate return to the eighth tier
OL,8,Fof English football after defeat in
OL,9,Fthe Southern Combination League play-
OL,10,Foff final.
OL,12,FThe Green Lions were heavily beaten 4-
OL,13,F1 by Peacehaven and Telscombe in front
OL,14,Fof more than a thousand fans at
OL,15,FVictoria Park earlier today (Saturday
OL,16,F23 May).
OL,18,FThe defeat came weeks after
OL,19,Fnegotiations on when and where to play
OL,20,Fthe final.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/4
