OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1779736281
OL,3,CGuernsey FC miss out on promotion
OL,4,Cafter play-off final defeat
OL,6,FGuernsey FC boss Tony Vance said:
OL,7,F"Naturally, we're disappointed and
OL,8,Ffrustrated. We didn't turn up on the
OL,9,Fday, and that's not taking anything
OL,10,Faway from Peacehaven as they deserved
OL,11,Fto win. I've enjoyed the season
OL,12,Foverall.
OL,14,F"We scored a lot of goals, but we just
OL,15,Ffell at the final hurdle today."
OL,17,FGFC were the favourites going into the
OL,18,Fgame, but were left stunned when
OL,19,FPeacehaven scored twice in the final
OL,20,Ffew minutes of the first half.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/4
