FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1779736281
OL,3,CGuernsey FC miss out on promotion
OL,4,Cafter play-off final defeat
OL,6,FAny hope of a comeback was punctured
OL,7,Fby an early second-half goal for the
OL,8,Fvisitors before they added a fourth
OL,9,Fshortly after the hour mark.
OL,11,FFin Du Port pulled one back for
OL,12,FGuernsey, but the damage had already
OL,13,Fbeen done.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/4
